title: Grateful Dead Live at Uptown Theater on 1981-02-28
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw, They Love Each Other, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Candyman, Little Red Rooster-> Big Railroad Blues, Althea, Let It Grow, Deal

Set 2

Cold Rain & Snow-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Ship of Fools, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Terrapin Station-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: One More Saturday Night
